ient` in HTTP/2 mode with push-promise handling enabled.\\n- Calls `ApplicationCall.push(\\\"/pushed\\\")` through Ktor’s public API.\\n- Verifies:\\n  - The root response is HTTP/2.\\n  - The pushed `/pushed` resource is received.\\n  - The expected response bodies are returned.\\n\\nThis path should exercise the remaining reflective call sites in `NettyHttp2Handler` involved in HTTP/2 push stream setup.\\n\\nPer instruction, I did not run or compile the tests locally.\", \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0a6704ccfacdad40016a28b8f80cc88197bd8974bbc73731c4\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 561, \"output\": 885, \"cacheRead\": 51712, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 53158, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"stop\", \"timestamp\": 1781053666317, \"responseId\": \"resp_0a6704ccfacdad40016a28b8e347f8819796439ae0da27febf\"}}\nhuman-intervention-logs/io.ktor:ktor-server-netty-jvm:3.2.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-10T01-08-12-245636Z.log:5430:[recv] {\"type\": \"turn_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"thinking\", \"thinking\": \"\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0a6704ccfacdad40016a28b8e4aa048197ab14542869eea452\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"content\\\":[],\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABqKLj4MOiWKaFizIm8HRmQJjby4QZECBWGVoQ9xhD8RDOapk8KsvhibVrxgakChuLrc8xzfJruJHManqadKFAAOhFpI8eFUQ08K0KfLyyiERVvCuM0tNapr-3azcyBa2uihbs9fuFN9xStuLXHbngS4bt38ZEgwYXJwV_sMVuk0YtTmY8VX-XJ9n0JsYvFHTTcgYPv82XeDBSzXs8fKS5WzLD32XvUzd2wi0vS-zMIZAVwwJyZWSp_KJ6yq0l8sIo0Rs9OwqxzlMuRIwGhlbAszfc3Rq6E1Md8DUitylPtMio35eTCck1Qjn1_SmARJts9XPorptpJGqDn5L7YBdRWflUM2Df7HyV8fEp66g4w4Fri0UdbE4TloAO8L2WKdlL5-WHdQ0GUd7GJXi8WHSPthWVuG8Ilp9OjduU76idYbh4opjtpn642sILbg_FR_UKMalX0xtk15XKNkaMF6N1VgOKnrE8W0TLuDyl3nFmK0xKrzGC-6G2Ne1vau