he root response and pushed response bodies.\\n\\nThis should allow Ktor’s `call.push(\\\"/pushed\\\")` path to proceed past `connection.remote().allowPushTo()` and exercise the reflective `NettyHttp2Handler` push-stream setup call sites.\", \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0a6704ccfacdad40016a28b98720188197b822584e7581777f\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 4788, \"output\": 915, \"cacheRead\": 47104, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 52807, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"stop\", \"timestamp\": 1781053807859, \"responseId\": \"resp_0a6704ccfacdad40016a28b97099e081979f200499812210a2\"}, \"toolResults\": []}\nhuman-intervention-logs/io.ktor:ktor-server-netty-jvm:3.2.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-10T01-08-12-245636Z.log:5669:  > Task :compileTestKotline: file:///home/jovan/Work/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/4496-289392a8/tests/src/io.ktor/ktor-server-netty-jvm/3.2.0/src/test/kotlin/io_ktor/ktor_server_netty_jvm/NettyHttp2HandlerTest.kt:175:50 Initializer type mismatch: expected 'DefaultHttp2Headers', actual 'Http2Headers!'.\nhuman-intervention-logs/io.ktor:ktor-server-netty-jvm:3.2.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-10T01-08-12-245636Z.log:5672:  > Task :compileTestKotlin FAILED\nhuman-intervention-logs/io.ktor:ktor-server-netty-jvm:3.2.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-10T01-08-12-245636Z.log:5725:[recv] {\"type\": \"message_start\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"When `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=io.ktor:ktor-server-netty-jvm:3.2.0` is ran this is the error:\\n> Task :tck-build-logic:extractPluginRequests UP-TO-DATE\\n> Task :tck-build-logic:generatePluginAdapters UP-TO-DATE\\n> Task :tck-build-logic:compileJava UP-TO-DATE